  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 67 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1\u00a0 -\u00a0 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd ; \u0b8f\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "67 people who tried to go to Australia by boat arrested - two remanded; Bail to others",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "67 people who tried to go to Australia illegally by boat have been arrested by the navy.",
        "Batticaloa - Illegal Australia by boat in a special round-up in the Wazaichenai waters.",
        "The marines said that the suspects were arrested while they were about to leave.",
        "Among them, except the driver of the boat and the agent who took the money from the people, others have been released on bail.",
        "Both of them have been remanded till the 22nd for further investigations."
      ],
